    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a dependable and comfortable driving experience. While the interior is clean and the exterior looks great overall, there are some minor cosmetic blemishes and light wear consistent with regular use. It is a reliable choice for anyone seeking a solid, road-ready vehicle that has many miles left to give.",
      "price": 33800.0,
